---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Social Media Growth" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Digital Content Strategy</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <img src="/social.jpg" alt="Content Strategy" class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-xl mb-8 bg-black p-8" />

    <div class="text-lg text-justify">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Growth Strategy</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I developed and executed a vertical video content strategy aimed at maximizing engagement and follower retention. By analyzing algorithm shifts and viewer retention metrics, I tailored content to capitalize on trending formats while maintaining a consistent brand voice.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Analytics & Optimization</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Data-Driven Content:</strong> Analyzed retention graphs to optimize video pacing, resulting in higher completion rates and algorithmic push.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Building:</strong> Implemented an active engagement strategy (replying to comments, Q&A features) to foster a loyal subscriber base.</li>
        <li><strong>Visual Identity:</strong> Maintained consistent editing standards and thumbnail aesthetics to strengthen brand recognition across platforms.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tech Stack</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="badge badge-ghost">TikTok Analytics</span>
        <span class="badge badge-ghost">CapCut Desktop</span>
        <span class="badge badge-ghost">SEO Optimization</span>
        <span class="badge badge-ghost">Trend Analysis</span>
      </div>
      
      </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
